race.comment: BRIEF STATEMENT (2) was close in a blanket finish when resuming here and has never missed the frame second-up. Loves this track and trip and looks a sharp improver despite the draw. BEAUMISTA (5) scored narrowly at Tamworth first-up and returns off a freshen. Won second-up last prep and looms as a key threat. ROCK 'N' REIGN (11) was strong late at Muswellbrook and is fitter now third-up. Draws perfectly and should be right in the mix. CAN DO IT (10) hit the line hard at Orange when resuming. Fitter now and is among the chances.
